       background: #c53030;\r\n            color: white;\r\n            text-align: center;\r\n            padding: 10px;\r\n            font-weight: bold;\r\n            letter-spacing: 1px;\r\n            font-size: 14px;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        ul {\r\n            margin: 5px 0;\r\n            padding-left: 20px;\r\n        }\r\n\r\n        li {\r\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\r\n        }\r\n    </style>\r\n</head>\r\n\r\n<body style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\r\n    <div class=\"sop-container\">\r\n        <div class=\"sop-header\">Booking Failure Handling Guidelines</div>\r\n        <h3 style=\"font-size: 16px; margin-top: 20px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;Most booking failures occur due to timeout exceptions. Check the latest error message (EM) on Slack.</h3>\r\n        <div class=\"sop-content\">\r\n            <table class=\"status-table\">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr style=\"background: #f8fafc; font-weight: bold;\">\r\n                        <td style=\"width: 40%;\">Scenario (Slack EM)</td>\r\n                        <td>Action Protocol</td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td><span class=\"error-tag\">SocketTimeoutException</span></td>\r\n                        <td>Wait <strong>a minimum of&nbsp;</strong><strong>2-3 hours&nbsp;</strong>before retrying automation.<div class=\"rule-box warning\"><strong>Do NOT retry immediately:</strong> Prevents system deadlocks and repeat loops.</div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td><span class=\"error-tag\">Error while calling API: transaction.id m&aacute;r l&eacute;tezik az adatb&aacute;zisban</span></td>\r\n                        <td>Fulfill <strong>m</strong><strong>anually&nbsp;</strong>on the portal. This cannot be re-automated.<div class=\"rule-box info\">Request a NEW card based on the portal price displayed, after converting to EUR. The default card will have insufficient funds and will FAIL.</div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            <div class=\"rule-box calm\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Ensure that the website is accessed in <strong>Hungarian</strong> and <strong>NOT English</strong>. This will allow you to book at a <strong>lesser price</strong>. You can use Google Translate if needed.</span></div>\r\n            <h3 style=\"font-size: 16px; margin-top: 20px;\">Manual Fulfillment &amp; Availability</h3>\r\n            <ul>\r\n                <li><strong>Slots Not Open:</strong> If the portal is not yet open for the date, move the booking to <strong>Future</strong> status. Monitor and book manually once open.</li>\r\n                <li><strong>Availability Logic:</strong> Never &quot;Hard Close&quot; slots based on portal status. API availability is <strong>unlimited</strong> and unrelated to portal sold-out statuses.</li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n            <div class=\"rule-box danger\"><strong>Critical:</strong> Portal unavailability &ne; API unavailability. Do NOT hard close API slots as per portal availability.</div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div class=\"footer-banner\">STRICTLY NO CANCELLATIONS OR MODIFICATIONS ALLOWED</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n</body>\r\n\r\n</html>",
