            "bookingInstructions": "<hr />\n<h3><span style=\"color: #b8312f;\">For Cancelation:</span> These tickets are NON-CANCELABLE.</h3>\n<hr />\n<p><br /><br /></p>\n<hr />\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h1><span style=\"background-color: #ccffcc;\"><strong>Please check the dates under all the sections before</strong></span><span style=\"background-color: #ccffcc;\"><strong>&nbsp;sharing alts</strong></span><span style=\"background-color: #ccffcc;\"><strong>.&nbsp;</strong></span></h1>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h1><span style=\"background-color: #ccffcc;\"><strong>Please check the time booked by the guest and book 'Morning' and 'Afternoon' session accordingly.&nbsp;</strong></span></h1>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;1. Click on the <strong><a href=\"https://tickets.spasbudapest.com/\">PORTAL LINK</a></strong>. Select the city of experience.</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em>Kindly change the language to English.</em></p>\n<p>2. Click on the correct product.<br />3. Select Weekday, Weekend or Holidays as per the date.<br />4. Select the date &amp; number of pax size. Add it to the basket and click on <em><strong>Buy</strong><strong><em>&nbsp;</em>items</strong></em><br />5. Fill in customer details - Name and Phone number<br /><strong>IMPORTANT</strong> - Please use volitand ID in customer details (<strong>NON-PARTNERED</strong>)<br />6. Payment Type - Pay with Bank Card (SimplePay)<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; Create an enett card and enter the card details on checkout page<br />7. Copy the Order Reference Number and search for tickets on Zendesk with the volitand ID entered in customer details in 2 min.<br />8. Download each ticket individually.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>The tickets should look like this:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://freeimage.host/i/HEnWxvn\"><img src=\"https://iili.io/HEnWxvn.md.jpg\" alt=\"HEnWxvn.md.jpg\" border=\"0\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
